title: Red Wave Rolls On
description: Fellas discuss Liz Cheney's primary defeat and the latest sports news before welcoming longtime NBC Sports reporter Michele Tafoya for a conversation. Pollsters Glen Bolger and Jarrett Lewis join to discuss the latest survey data and their new project with today's sponsor, Americans For Prosperity: www.personaloption.com
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Glen Bolger, Jarrett Lewis, Michele Tafoya, Michael Duncan, Comfortably Smug, Josh Holmes, John Ashbrook)
